01,"uid":223260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:10:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1751c7e270f263e12ec718088f79f212d8ed54b6","tid":1556001,"uid":223260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"566a8407d8b493372ad428e417b4809d4a6ee59b","tid":1556001,"uid":305883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:59:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZguU1VW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZguU1VW.png&h=c205dd61&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n劣質圖support"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:10:25.000Z","msg":"多謝你"},{"pid":"62ccf455752d9d5bab91cbf7250809f7f4f8b607","tid":1556001,"uid":223260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:13:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c207012b54d2d3636be80630ec404e8e2ffe61e5","tid":1556001,"uid":97716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:35:24.000Z","msg":"PUSH 開TG!!"},{"pid":"3eca79438e280c64310d593ae6583d111d5cb9ff","tid":1556001,"uid":239250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:41:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a21590e840bb744dce053030904b71ae8d28041a","tid":1556001,"uid":282115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:48:08.000Z","msg":"咁短時間做全球？"},{"pid":"1ef338911a51b75949ce9541e7d843977983ab07","tid":1556001,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T12:26:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d6665dfb72064b71e606310c756dc9b71a6e427","tid":1556001,"uid":278786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T18:23:27.000Z","msg":"如何做到有一百萬人以上，對和理非而言，最重要是不用申請不反對通知書而且有合法途徑。否則乜文宣都無用。<br />\n有條橋，就是抄何妖，佢話921清潔香港不用申請不反對通知書，仲串到撤銷遊行申請。<br />\n咁佢無被人拉無人告，心理上就可以宣傳：我地9.29搞的都是清潔香港行動，沿港島電車路線，人人執拉圾。<br />\n<br />\n人流控制方面：<br />\n可以呼籲港島人在自己區清潔；<br />\n九龍東人在鰂魚涌的香港殯儀館（象徵送中）以東，新界東人在鰂魚涌以西;<br />\n九龍西人在中環遮打花園以西，新界西人在中環以東。<br />\n<br />\n另一個重點，係需要有號召力的人或機構呼籲，大肆宣傳，俾和理非感覺既合法又多人陪，咁就安心參加。<br />\n<br />\n利申：和理非"}]}